                      ],
                      "text": "Teaser dan Trailer",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "Teaser Kisah: Yaksha, Sang Adeptus Pelindung",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/23/237301566/90f7b599b4d7f65c3edf3844d9cf3f04_5140932463371261091.png"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "27 Januari 2021",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Alatus — Raja Bersayap Emas yang juga dijuluki Conqueror of Demons. Tidak ada yang mengetahui asal-usulnya, dan juga tidak ada yang mengetahui tujuan akhirnya.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Hanya pada malam musim semi, saat lentera-lentera diterbangkan, penduduk Liyue yang melihat ke arah Guyun akan berseru: \"Lihat, Vigilant Yaksha sedang memburu para iblis!\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Atau mereka akan mendengar suara seruling dari rawa-rawa, tetapi saat dicari, tidak ada seorang pun di sana. Mereka pun akan berseru: \"Para Yaksha sedang memanggil rekan-rekan lamanya kembali ke kampung halaman mereka.\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 172, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "HoYoLAB:",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(55, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "https://www.hoyolab.com/article/152781",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "Teaser Kisah: Memori Lama yang Tersisa",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/23/237301566/68227850eb221e54dc2b6c91f89e1436_291937187263281196.png"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "2 Juni 2022",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Setelah krisis berakhir, orang-orang akan pergi satu demi satu, ada yang dalam renungan, ada yang dalam kepuasan.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Tapi Xiao mengundangmu untuk berbincang, bercerita tentang memori seorang Yaksha yang telah dibangkitkan ....",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 172, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "HoYoLAB:",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(55, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "https://www.hoyolab.com/article/5121496",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "Teaser Kisah: Gema Suara di Hati",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/16/170306649/d9ad26954d1ce9e0a40f196b72450232_6422431082510597348.png"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "21 Januari 2023",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Seperti kepulan asap yang menghilang dalam sekejap mata, seperti tangkai yang mengambang tanpa akar.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Aliran air mengalir, menyapu butiran debu yang ada.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 172, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "HoYoLAB:",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(55, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "https://www.hoyolab.com/article/15209511",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "Trailer Versi 4.4 \"Pesona Corak Angin Musim Semi\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/21/237301566/2b4ba05abf8ef2585a4d3c2128084609_3450904720678795680.png"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "19 Januari 2024",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Musim semi tiba lebih awal, hewan keberuntungan datang menyapa, membawa serta angin keberuntungan tinggi di atas awan.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Bagaikan bangau liar, layangan warna-warni membubung tinggi, aliran sungai bergerak melewati lembah tempat harta karun tersembunyi.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 172, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "HoYoLAB:",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(55, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "https://www.hoyolab.com/article/24445730",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "Adegan Animasi Pesona Corak Angin Musim Semi \"Layangan Berkibar di Tengah Angin\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/26/237301566/bfc85aae7acd8f1bbb45bcab95f44bcd_8387963249736878829.png"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "9 Februari 2024",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Perayaan seperti ini mengisi hidup kita dengan momen kebahagiaan yang langka. Tapi akankah kita bertemu lagi setelah kembang apinya padam?",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Jika kita bisa tanyakan kepada angin yang bertiup sebelum musim semi tiba, ia mungkin bisa memberitahukan kapan mereka yang mengembara akan kembali, dan kapan kita bisa berbincang lagi di bawah terang bulan.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 172, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "HoYoLAB:",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(55, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "https://www.hoyolab.com/article/25102032",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
